snippet.title: Paper Dolls - Launch Trailer｜PS VR
snippet.description:
Paper Dolls is a first-person VR horror game with a hint of Asian culture. The story begins with a man driving his daughter to his estranged wife's house. Suddenly, his car crashed and he found himself, daughter-less, in a deserted ancient Chinese house.
Explore the ancient ruins of the late Qing dynasty and search for your daughter.

https://www.winkingworks.com/publishing/index.html
